            <section xml:id="da/d9b/group___r_t_c___group12_1gaad434ed2a268f05662f0613e8e9717f3">
                <title>ErrorStatus RTC_SynchroShiftConfig (uint32_t RTC_ShiftAdd1S, uint32_t RTC_ShiftSubFS)</title> <emphasis>Configures the Synchronization Shift Control Settings.</emphasis>
                
<para><formalpara><title>Note: </title>

<para>When REFCKON is set, firmware must not write to Shift control register </para>
</formalpara>

                <formalpara>
                    <title/>
                    <table frame="all">
                        <title>Parameters</title>
                        <tgroup cols="2" align="left" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
                        <tbody>
                            <row>
                                <entry>RTC_ShiftAdd1S</entry>
                                <entry>
<para>: Select to add or not 1 second to the time Calendar. This parameter can be one of the following values : <itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>RTC_ShiftAdd1S_Set : Add one second to the clock calendar. </para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para>RTC_ShiftAdd1S_Reset: No effect. </para>
</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry>RTC_ShiftSubFS, :</entry>
                                <entry>
<para>Select the number of Second Fractions to Substitute. This parameter can be one any value from 0 to 0x7FFF. </para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                        </tbody>
                        </tgroup>
                    </table>
                </formalpara>
                
                <formalpara>
                    <title/>
                    <table frame="all">
                        <title>Parameters</title>
                        <tgroup cols="2" align="left" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
                        <tbody>
                            <row>
                                <entry>An</entry>
                                <entry>
<para>ErrorStatus enumeration value:<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>SUCCESS: RTC Shift registers are configured</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para>ERROR: RTC Shift registers are not configured </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                        </tbody>
                        </tgroup>
                    </table>
                </formalpara>
                </para>

